# React / TypeScript

## Stack

React 18+, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, Vite. State: Zustand or colocated React state.

## Structure

- `src/features/{context,checklist,buddy-check}/` — feature modules
- `src/components/ui/` — shared presentational components
- `src/lib/` — storage, checklist engine helpers
- `src/content/templates/` — checklist template data

## Patterns

- Prefer function components and named exports for features
- Typed props; avoid `any`
- Derive checklist UI from typed `ChecklistItem[]`, never inline string arrays in JSX
- Keep components thin; merge logic in `lib/checklist-engine.ts` (or equivalent)

## Do not

- Add UI libraries (MUI, Chakra) without decision in `agent-runs/`
- Fetch remote APIs in MVP
- Create abstractions used only once
